WEBVTT

1
00:00:56.141 --> 00:00:57.208
MOM: <i>At the end of high school.</i>

2
00:00:57.308 --> 00:01:00.712
<i>I fell in love with a substitute
English teacher.</i>

3
00:01:00.812 --> 00:01:02.839
<i>It was quite a scandal.</i>

4
00:01:02.939 --> 00:01:06.092
Corin didn't start
out a bad guy. though.

5
00:01:06.192 --> 00:01:09.487
We were together about 10 years
and we had two kids. (CLICKS TONGUE)

6
00:01:09.612 --> 00:01:13.224
And then he fell in love
with someone in a Starbucks.

7
00:01:13.324 --> 00:01:16.978
and moved to Palo Alto. California.

8
00:01:17.078 --> 00:01:21.524
Kind of severed relations
with the three of us.

9
00:01:21.624 --> 00:01:25.737
My parents. if I were defending them.
which I'm not.

10
00:01:25.837 --> 00:01:29.340
had said. back in the day.
that he had an "impatient eye."

11
00:01:29.466 --> 00:01:31.509
They didn't like him. (CHUCKLES)

12
00:01:31.634 --> 00:01:35.789
Week I left. things escalated.

13
00:01:35.889 --> 00:01:39.434
My parents cursed at me.
which was. like. crazy unusual.

14
00:01:41.186 --> 00:01:44.547
And it ended. one afternoon.
very badly. (SMACKS LIPS)

15
00:01:44.647 --> 00:01:49.694
I left at 19. haven't spoken
to my parents in 15 years.

16
00:01:50.737 --> 00:01:52.405
Whatever. That's just the history.

17
00:01:54.199 --> 00:01:58.061
<i>Recently. my parents
looked me up on the Internet.</i>

18
00:01:58.161 --> 00:01:59.771
<i>Asked to meet their grandchildren.</i>

19
00:01:59.871 --> 00:02:01.748
<i>Spend a week with them.</i>

20
00:02:01.873 --> 00:02:04.834
<i>I looked my parents up.
they have a counseling website.</i>

21
00:02:05.043 --> 00:02:06.194
(CHUCKLES)

22
00:02:06.294 --> 00:02:07.462
People love them.

23
00:02:07.629 --> 00:02:11.257
Ironically. they counsel people.
which is a hoot.

24
00:02:11.382 --> 00:02:14.761
Whatever. I told the kids.
They said they wanted to go.

25
00:02:14.886 --> 00:02:16.121
I told them I didn't want them to go.

26
00:02:16.221 --> 00:02:18.431
They said they were gonna
go anyway. (CHUCKLES)

27
00:02:18.556 --> 00:02:20.642
They're brats. What can I tell you?

28
00:02:21.893 --> 00:02:25.630
<i>And my 15-year-old wants to make
